Check readline input

Source: R/interactive.R
readline_check.Rd

Check readline input

readline_check(prompt, type = c("numeric", "integer", "length",
  "minlength", "maxlength", "exact", "grep"), compare = NULL, ...)

Arguments

prompt

the prompt for readline
type

what type of check to perform, one of c("numeric", "character", "length", "minlength", "maxlength", "exact", "grep")
compare

the comparator for exact and (min|max)length types
...

other arguments to pass to grep

Value

the validated result of readline

Examples

readline_check("Type a number: ", "numeric")
